Tao file:
- index.html => web server => tu nhan file index.html lam file goc

while space: 
- dau cach (space)
- tab
- new line (xuong dong) => la 1 ky tu

=> html => white space => bo qua

Cau truc cua trang html:
- doctype: loai tai lieu: <!DOCTYPE html>
- html:
	- head: dau
		+ title: Tieu de
		+ meta:
		+ link:
	- body: than
		+ div: vung tren trang web
			+ tao ra 1 vung tren trang web
			+ chua cac the khac
		+ p : doan van (paragraph)
		+ h (h1->h6) heading
		+ ul => unorder list
		+ ol => order list
		+ li => phan tu danh sach
		+ img : image - hinh anh
		+ br : break => xuong hang
		+ span : the danh dau => dung de viet css
			=> khong co y nghia ket thuc
		+ a : lien ket: click vao => chay den trang khac

		+ header
		+ section
		+ sidebar
		+ footer
		=> giong the div => tao ra mot vung tren trang web

		Form: o nhap du lieu
			+ input
				+ text: o nhap chu
				+ password
				+ email:
				+ button
				+ submit: gui du lieu di
				+ reset: xoa du lieu cua form
				+ checkbox
				+ radio
				+ number
				+ color
			+ select:
				+ option
			+ label:
				Nhan

Phan chia:
	+ The hien thi noi dung: p, h, li, img, a
	+ The dung de bao boc: div, section, header, footer, form => the giao dien

=> the giao dien chua cac the noi dung
=> the giao dien => ko duoc nam trong the noi dung

+ Block va inline:
	+ Block: Dang khoi: minh no nam tren 1 dong
		+ div, p, h, form, ul, li, ol

	+ Inline: Tren dong: nam cung dong voi cac the khac
		+ con lai: button, input, select, span

=> thanh phan block => khong the nam trong thanh phan inline

Bai tap:
Tao mot trang html => viet het tat ca cac the da hoc => xem